y_Firewall)\n    O ->> N : Streamed tokens / chunked response\n    loop while streaming tokens\n        N ->> C : Forward token chunks (Security_OAuth2)\n    end\n\n    N ->> L : Access + security events (Security_Firewall)\n    P ->> L : Auth events (Security_Encryption)\n    F ->> L : Policy evaluation results (Security_ZeroTrust)\n    O ->> L : Inference metrics (Security_OAuth2)\n\n    N ->> C : 200 OK (Security_OAuth2) OR controlled 4xx with safe message\n",
